ZecBus — for agents
===================
The site drives the winbit32 gateway: REST/MCP under https://mcp.winbit32.com
(/v1/zec/bus). Find the next departure, then board it with a shielded deposit;
the gateway serves CORS so a browser-side agent can drive it.

Finding and boarding a departure happens in the ZecBus web app / the gateway
MCP (both under Links) — there is no in-client gopher action for it yet, so
Actions is omitted rather than dressing up a plain link as one.
